g.title: j3951173461
g.text: You’ve got to be the strongest hero in the Hex. I mean, considering everyone here is partly metal, you're definitely not one to be messed with.

g.title: j471254272
g.text: I’ve been thinking, out of everyone on the team, your instinct to always look out for others makes you the most heroic of us all.

g.title: j2746139037
g.text: haha

g.title: j2073451041
g.text: +5 Chemistry

g.title: j821350594
g.text: u sound just like Amir

g.title: j974680102
g.text: <RETRO_EMOJI_HEART>

g.title: j3199649847
g.text: First time in my life I've been told that.

g.title: j4147701155
g.text: Why thank you. How so?

g.title: j21259857
g.text: Really? What makes you say that?

g.title: j1523729890
g.text: Is that a compliment?

g.title: j4261118901
g.text: really? but u two are so alike ;)

g.title: j1087562513
g.text: +5 Chemistry

g.title: j2689969994
g.text: it's just that when Amir first joined the Hex, he’d joke about me being this superhero

g.title: j1133849504
g.text: of course it is!

g.title: j3964944978
g.text: ... and him being my sidekick

g.title: j3787744522
g.text: it was sweet but also a little sad

g.title: j2064676919
g.text: That’s surprising. Amir always seems so confident.

g.title: j930092719
g.text: A sidekick, huh? That doesn’t sound like the Amir I know now. What changed?

g.title: j1930107133
g.text: Sad? I thought you two were close.

g.title: j1860424010
g.text: it took time. Amir joined us without any military experience, so the fighting was overwhelming for him

g.title: j2481983367
g.text: oh, we are! Amir’s my best friend. some of my favorite memories are us in the arcade, gaming and rocking out to On-lyne

g.title: j2393311701
g.text: he just needed to see that being a hero wasn’t all about combat

g.title: j2981946021
g.text: but the whole sidekick thing? I could tell he felt... small.

g.title: j1839235214
g.text: I always knew that a hacker as great as him could be a hero in his own way

g.title: j1554876604
g.text: So what changed for him? He doesn’t seem like anyone's sidekick now.

g.title: j3987779076
g.text: And you played a big part in helping him realize that, didn’t you?

g.title: j827734956
g.text: I can’t take all the credit, but I was there when he had his breakthrough.

g.title: j4204595734
g.text: one day, I caught this wild broadcast from an On-lyne fan who'd pieced together some shady details about HitMaker (that's On-lyne's label)

g.title: j449422091
g.text: she was basically begging for someone to help them, and Amir jumped in without hesitation

g.title: j1319357804
g.text: How'd Amir get involved in something like that?

g.title: j2479701415
g.text: Amir? I thought it would have been you running to On-lyne's rescue.

g.title: j2605946905
g.text: This sounds like a legendary Aoi-Amir team-up to me.

g.title: j2400266515
g.text: I showed him the broadcast. Amir took care of the rest!

g.title: j101121848
g.text: weeell it was a team effort. u could say I was his sidekick ^_^

g.title: j3891058668
g.text: +5 Chemistry

g.title: j1400324118
g.text: he hacked into their manager's emails and uncovered a mess of deals with the Scaldra. they’d been cloning the band and putting them in danger, all covered up by their management

g.title: j1441489935
g.text: a super-fan joining forces with a super-hacker? nothing could stop us!

g.title: j2526725817
g.text: bleh!

g.title: j4248489345
g.text: without Amir’s skills, none of that would’ve come to light

g.title: j1008249574
g.text: Wow. That’s incredible. Amir really uncovered all that?

g.title: j2013313565
g.text: You know, if it's true that knowledge is power, hackers really are powerful.

g.title: j3648039705
g.text: u bet. the whole ordeal totally helped him realized he wasn’t just a sidekick. he was a hero in his own right ^_^

g.title: j2168270537
g.text: And you still get to rock out in the arcade together

g.title: j3256611945
g.text: As if there could ever have been any doubt.

g.title: j3038918893
g.text: just two heroes taking a break!

g.title: j1424291691
g.text: right?

g.title: j3578125693
g.text: ur a hero too, u know <RETRO_EMOJI_HEART>

g.title: j826387642
g.text: That means a lot coming from you.

g.title: j2286242704
g.text: Makes me feel awfully good hearing that.

g.title: j1976118430
g.text: You charmer.

g.title: j2645712573
g.text: +5 Chemistry

g.title: j3828291161
g.text: +5 Chemistry

g.title: j3363402299
g.text: guilty ;)

g.title: j2003925143
g.text: oh u <RETRO_EMOJI_HEART>

g.text: good! <RETRO_EMOJI_HEART>
